Petr Cech on &Ouml;zil and Alexis: &quot;I think it is important to show them how much we need them in the team and how much we want to win.&quot;<br />
<br />
Cech: &quot;If they see that we are competitive and everybody is ready to win things together, then this will make their decision easier.&quot;

Wenger on Iwobi: &quot;He is gaining in confidence. If he keeps that kind of spirit he has at the moment, he can go much higher. That's my wish.&quot;<br />
<br />
Wenger: &quot;He is more comfortable in the team, but I think Alex Iwobi, above all his talent, is a guy who has a fantastic team attitude.&quot;

&Ouml;zil: &quot;I have changed a few things in the last year, my diet and training. This helps me to regenerate faster and reduces vulnerability.&quot;<br />
<br />
&Ouml;zil on winning German Player of the Year: &quot;I've remained injury-free for the most part &amp; I feel very comfortable in London now as well.&quot;
